snippet.title: Men in Black gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Men in Black, PC game produced by Gremlin Interactive in 1997: https://www.squakenet.com/game/men-in-black

Excellent action game, kind of survival horror game with some similarity to Resident Evil. Playing through the first couple of stages.

Played through old Windows XP real machine.
Recorded with full original sound.
